<% if @plan == "friend" %>
<h1 class="center">Thanks</h1>

<p class="lead">We appreciate your support.</p>

<p>Your subscription as a friend of Ruby Together will be charged automatically every month, and we'll send another email with the receipt for your first payment.</p>

<p>Ruby Together is a trade association, not a charity, so your contribution is probably not tax-deductible. (Ask your accountant to be sure, though. YMMV.)
</p>

<p>If you want to change your name or email address, you can <%= link_to "manage your membership", membership_url(token: @token) %>.</p>

<% else %>
<h1 class="center">Welcome</h1>

<p class="lead">Thanks for joining Ruby Together.</p>

<p>Your membership dues will be charged automatically every month, and we'll send another email with the receipt for your first payment.</p>

<p>Ruby Together is a 501(c)(6) non-profit organization, and membership dues are tax-deductible by anyone using Ruby as part of their business. (Ask your accountant to be sure, may not apply outside the US. YMMV.)
</p>

<p>In order to be credited in our <%= link_to "list of members", members_url %>, just fill in your name on the <%= link_to "manage your membership", membership_url(token: @token) %> page.</p>

<% end %>
